metadata.name: Forgotten Station
metadata.description:
Early morning in an empty station 
surrounded by furry friend and flying spirits 
reminiscing our sweet memories together.

"Forgotten Station" is my first Open Edition piece, a piece dedicated to all friends who have been through all the ups and downs in this space together. Like an empty station, we might be “forgotten” somehow somewhere. Nonetheless, with the support & blessings of each other, we will continue to swim through every storm courageously.
